OsKp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fz0TOsKp.jpg&h=3202d5f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KtwPcgP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FKtwPcgP.jpg&h=91532001&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年7月在中國bilibili上舉行的「鋼彈G會發佈會」上，宣布即將在中國上海打造《機動<br />\n戰士鋼彈SEED》實物大「自由鋼彈」。發表會後經過約10個月，現在這尊實物大自由鋼彈<br />\n終於在今（26）日進行安全祈願儀式，並預計在4月28日隨著新商場開放正式亮相。<br />\n <br />\n萬代南夢宮中國在微博上表示，本次自由鋼彈是日本海外首次1：1真實還原的18公尺立像<br />\n。早在前幾天包括身體、翅膀、手臂等登已經安裝完成，今日安裝的重頭戲就在自由鋼<br />\n彈的頭部，並同步舉行安全祈願儀式。<br />\n <br />\n目前自由鋼彈僅剩下腳部就完成全體施工，而腳部安裝作業預計今晚會進行。萬代南夢宮<br />\n中國指出，雖然自由鋼彈本體將隨著上海金橋啦啦寶都於 4 月 28 日開幕時開放讓粉絲<br />\n參觀，不過開放後仍會進行燈光測試，預計 5 月 28 日會有一場精采的表演秀。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://game.nownews.com/news/20210426/3293139/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.nownews.com%2Fnews%2F20210426%2F3293139%2F&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepDvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=0f05a793\" target=\"_blank\">https://game.nownews.com/news/20210426/3293139/</a>"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />痴撚線，好拎唔拎，搵架freedom"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:10:00.000Z","msg":"要改名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:30:37.000Z","msg":"國安gundam<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75114d4ce699216a0b5ce49307e34ff9ef6f86f","tid":2504964,"uid":143608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T09:31:10.000Z","msg":"咱們的是具有中國特色的自由高達<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"